# 🔗 4. Connecter ton frontend au backend

Dans ton `script.js` :

```js
const API_URL = "https://api.mathphix.com";

fetch(`${API_URL}/api/faq`, {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ question: "Explique les fractions" })
})
.then(res => res.json())
.then(data => console.log(data));
```

---

# ⚠️ 5. Important (sinon ça casse)

## 🔹 Activer CORS côté backend

Dans ton `server/index.js` :

```js
import cors from "cors";

app.use(cors({
  origin: "https://www.mathphix.com"
}));
```

---

## 🔹 Installer cors

```bash
npm install cors
```

